title: Channel-Specific Personas
---
Bind different agent templates and system prompts to different channels: the Telegram channel gets the casual assistant persona; the Slack channel gets the code review template; the Discord channel gets the research assistant. 'clawq agents bind research-agent --channel discord'. Partial support exists (agent template bindings) but not per-channel system prompt overrides or automatic persona switching on message routing.